                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1201433</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本著名的电子游戏制作商 Konami 于「Xbox 合作伙伴预览（Xbox Partner Peview）」展示会上，公布了早前宣布重制的游戏《Metal Gear Solid Delta: Snake Eater》（潜龙谍影 Delta：食蛇者）的新预告片，片中写实精美的画面由最新一代 Unreal Engine 5 游戏引擎重新展示。</p><p>Konami 在游戏预告片中展示了过去潜龙系列中的标志性玩法，而主角「Snake」将只身空降深入危险的热带丛林与山岳地带。面对严酷险恶的自然环境，以及虎视眈眈的动物与敌人，一边求生、一边任务。</p><p>影片的结尾更确认实机游戏画面由最新一代 Unreal Engine 5 游戏引擎重新制作。其中展示的多个游戏环境和动物，例如在草地上滑行的蛇、水里的蟹、用手枪攻击对方的画面都相当精美。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="size-medium wp-image-1201438 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-12.16.54-694x367.png" alt="" width="694" height="367" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-12.16.54-694x367.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-12.16.54-1280x677.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-12.16.54-768x406.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-12.16.54.png 1520w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1201439 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-12.17.04-694x359.png" alt="" width="694" height="359" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-12.17.04-694x359.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-12.17.04-1280x662.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-12.17.04-768x397.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-12.17.04.png 1508w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1201440 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-12.17.53-694x367.png" alt="" width="694" height="367" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-12.17.53-