            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1201423</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 发布的公告指，Apple Watch Series 9 及 Apple Watch Ultra 2 上「全新轻点两下」手势 （Double Tap Gesture） 现于 watchOS 10.1 登场，只要将符合机款的 Apple Watch 更新到最新版本都能使用。</p><p>「Double Tap Gesture」功能用于用户其中一只手不方便时，只需在佩戴智能手表的手透过「互点拇指和食指两下」的动作，无需触碰显示器的情况下就能单手控制手表。</p><p>目前 watchOS 10.1 己于 Apple Watch Series 4 及其后最新型号上推出，装置须配对运行 iOS 17 的 iPhone XS 及更新的型号。</p><p>此功能可帮助用户执行不同的 watchOS app 及通知等动作，包括开启「智慧型叠放」，并从中卷动小工具；接听或结束通话；以及播放及暂停音乐；延迟闹钟；查看通知中的讯息、以重复轻按两下翻阅较长的通知、以「听写」回复及传送讯息等。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1201425 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-10.51.20-694x381.png" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-10.51.20-694x381.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-10.51.20-1280x703.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-10.51.20-768x422.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-10.51.20-1536x844.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-26-10.51.20.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />（图片来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/newsroom/2023/10/apple-watch-double-tap-gesture-now-available-with-watchos-10-1/">apple</a>）</p><p>而「Double Tap Gesture」功能透过神经网络引擎，运用机械学习演算法去侦测手部食指与拇指重复开合两下的微细动作，以及血液流动的变化。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/newsroom/2023/10/apple-watch-double-tap-gesture-now-available-with-watchos-10-1/">apple</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
